---
import { asset } from '../../utils/assets';

// Hero section con contenido optimizado para SEO y Core Web Vitals
---

<section class="hero" id="inicio">
	<div class="hero-bg">
		<img 
			src={asset("/img/hero.png")}
			alt="Fachada Clínica Dental Villajoyosa 99"
			class="hero-image"
			loading="eager"
			fetchpriority="high"
		/>
	</div>
	<div class="hero-overlay"></div>
	<div class="container hero-content">
		<div class="hero-inner">
			<h1>Tu sonrisa, en manos expertas</h1>
			<div class="hero-bottom">
				<div class="hero-text">
					<p>Los mejores profesionales y la medicina más avanzada nos diferencian de los demás. Porque lo más importante para nosotros eres tú, con nuestra atención individualizada te ayudaremos a permanecer siempre saludable y feliz.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="hero-buttons">
					<a href="tel:+34917988669" class="btn-primary">Llámanos ahora</a>
					<a href="#contacto" class="btn-secondary">Pide una cita</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<a href="#stats" class="scroll-indicator" aria-label="Scroll hacia abajo">
		<svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
			<path d="M12 5v14M5 12l7 7 7-7"/>
		</svg>
	</a>
</section>

<style>
	.hero {
		position: relative;
		height: 100vh;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	
	.hero-bg {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		z-index: 0;
	}
	
	.hero-bg .hero-image {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
		object-position: center 25%;
		display: block;
		filter: blur(2px);
	}
	
	.hero-overlay {
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
		z-index: 1;
	}
	
	.hero-content {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 2;
		height: 100%;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
	}
	
	.hero-inner {
		width: 100%;
	}
	
	.hero-inner h1 {
		font-size: 48px;
		color: white;
		font-family: var(--ff-head);
		font-weight: 700;
		line-height: 1.1;
		margin: 0 0 2rem 0;
		text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
	}
	
	.hero-bottom {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		gap: 3rem;
		align-items: center;
	}
	
	.hero-text p {
		font-size: 17px;
		color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
		font-family: var(--ff-body);
		line-height: 1.7;
		margin: 0;
		text-shadow: 1px 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
	}
	
	.hero-buttons {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		justify-content: center;
	}
	
	.hero-buttons .btn-primary,
	.hero-buttons .btn-secondary {
		padding: 0.875rem 1.75rem;
		border-radius: 6px;
		font-size: 15px;
		font-weight: 600;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition: all 0.2s ease;
		white-space: nowrap;
	}
	
	.hero-buttons .btn-primary {
		background: var(--c-primary);
		color: white;
		border: 2px solid var(--c-primary);
	}
	
	.hero-buttons .btn-primary:hover {
		background: white;
		color: var(--c-primary);
	}
	
	.hero-buttons .btn-secondary {
		background: transparent;
		color: white;
		border: 2px solid white;
	}
	
	.hero-buttons .btn-secondary:hover {
		background: white;
		color: var(--c-ink);
	}
	
	.scroll-indicator {
		position: absolute;
		bottom: 2rem;
		left: 50%;
		transform: translateX(-50%);
		z-index: 3;
		color: white;
		text-decoration: none;
		animation: bounce 2s infinite;
	}
	
	.scroll-indicator svg {
		display: block;
	}
	
	@keyframes bounce {
		0%, 20%, 50%, 80%, 100% {
			transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(0);
		}
		40% {
			transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-10px);
		}
		60% {
			transform: translateX(-50%) translateY(-5px);
		}
	}
	
	@media (max-width: 767px) {
		.hero {
			height: 100vh;
			min-height: 100vh;
			padding: 2rem 0;
		}
		
		.scroll-indicator {
			bottom: 1.5rem;
		}
		
		.hero-inner h1 {
			font-size: 32px;
			margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
		}
		
		.hero-bottom {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 2rem;
		}
		
		.hero-text p {
			font-size: 15px;
		}
		
		.hero-buttons {
			flex-direction: column;
			gap: 0.75rem;
		}
		
		.hero-buttons .btn-primary,
		.hero-buttons .btn-secondary {
			text-align: center;
		}
	}
</style>

